    public class RogLastSearchDialog
extends RogPublicSearchDialog
implements com.emc.d2fs.dctm.dialogs.ID2Dialog
    Custom Public search dialog class supporting D2QueryFormConfig templates with FreeMarker syntax used in DQL. Allows to initialize the dialog controls with parameters of a previously executed search.
